# Discord bridge bot — OPTIONAL second file beside the Relay API `.env`.
#
# Load order:
#   1) Repo root `.env` (shared secrets: RELAY_DISCORD_INGEST_HMAC_SECRET, RELAY_DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN, etc.)
#   2) This file (`discord-bot/.env`) — only fills keys that aren’t already set.
#
# Do NOT leave lines like RELAY_DISCORD_INGEST_HMAC_SECRET= with nothing after "=" — that pins an empty
# value and used to shadow the repo when load order was wrong. Prefer deleting this file entirely if root
# has everything.

# Overrides (only if needed):
# DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=
# DISCORD_APPLICATION_ID=
# DISCORD_CLIENT_ID=

# Optional: slash commands scoped to one guild for instant Discord updates during dev:
# DISCORD_GUILD_ID=

# Optional: Relay HTTP base when not default:
# RELAY_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787

# Optional: reply in-channel when ingest 404 (channel not linked yet):
# RELAY_DISCORD_REPLY_ON_404=1
